snippet.title: Moving Houses PC Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming this fall to PC via Steam and Itch.io 

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2831060/Moving_Houses/
Itchio: https://gordgames.itch.io/moving-houses

Enjoy this silly physics-based first-person game about moving on. Pack up your life and toss it in the van. Be neat, be careful, or be a chaos goblin. The choice is yours!
